#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.19"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.19:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.19:0.2"
msgid "2. Rathakāravagga"
msgstr "2. The Chariotmaker"

# What it takes to run a successful business; and what it takes to increase in the skillful.
#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.19:0.3"
msgid "19. Paṭhamapāpaṇikasutta"
msgstr "19. A Shopkeeper (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.19:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Tīhi, bhikkhave, aṅgehi samannāgato pāpaṇiko abhabbo anadhigataṃ vā bhogaṃ "
"adhigantuṃ, adhigataṃ vā bhogaṃ phātiṃ kātuṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, a shopkeeper who has three factors is unable to acquire more "
"wealth or to increase the wealth they’ve already acquired."

msgctxt "an3.19:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi tīhi?"
msgstr "What three?"

#. VAR: majjhanhikasamayaṃ → majjhantikaṃ samayaṃ (bj) | majjhantikasamayaṃ (s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an3.19:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, pāpaṇiko pubbaṇhasamayaṃ na sakkaccaṃ kammantaṃ adhiṭṭhāti, "
"majjhanhikasamayaṃ na sakkaccaṃ kammantaṃ adhiṭṭhāti, sāyanhasamayaṃ na "
"sakkaccaṃ kammantaṃ adhiṭṭhāti."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a shopkeeper doesn’t carefully apply themselves to their work in "
"the morning, at midday, and in the afternoon."

#. VAR: phātiṃ kātuṃ → phātikattuṃ (bj) | phātikātuṃ (s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an3.19:1.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, tīhi aṅgehi samannāgato pāpaṇiko abhabbo anadhigataṃ "
"vā bhogaṃ adhigantuṃ, adhigataṃ vā bhogaṃ phātiṃ kātuṃ."
msgstr ""
"A shopkeeper who has these three factors is unable to acquire more wealth or "
"to increase the wealth they’ve already acquired."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.19:2.1"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tīhi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu abhabbo "
"anadhigataṃ vā kusalaṃ dhammaṃ adhigantuṃ, adhigataṃ vā kusalaṃ dhammaṃ "
"phātiṃ kātuṃ."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, a mendicant who has three factors is unable to acquire more "
"skillful qualities or to increase the skillful qualities they’ve already "
"acquired."

msgctxt "an3.19:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi tīhi?"
msgstr "What three?"

# Note: Not “object of concentration” as BB has it. The samadhinimitta is elsewhere defined as satipatthana, i.e. the meditation that you do in order to get into jhana. Nimitta, here and elsewhere in the suttas, means neither “object” nor “meditative vision”, but “cause”.
msgctxt "an3.19:2.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu pubbaṇhasamayaṃ na sakkaccaṃ samādhinimittaṃ "
"adhiṭṭhāti, majjhanhikasamayaṃ na sakkaccaṃ samādhinimittaṃ adhiṭṭhāti, "
"sāyanhasamayaṃ na sakkaccaṃ samādhinimittaṃ adhiṭṭhāti."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant doesn’t carefully apply themselves to a meditation "
"subject as a basis of immersion in the morning, at midday, and in the "
"afternoon."

msgctxt "an3.19:2.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, tīhi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu abhabbo anadhigataṃ "
"vā kusalaṃ dhammaṃ adhigantuṃ, adhigataṃ vā kusalaṃ dhammaṃ phātiṃ kātuṃ."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant who has these three factors is unable to acquire more skillful "
"qualities or to increase the skillful qualities they’ve already acquired."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.116"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an3.19:3.1"
msgid ""
"Tīhi, bhikkhave, aṅgehi samannāgato pāpaṇiko bhabbo anadhigataṃ vā bhogaṃ "
"adhigantuṃ, adhigataṃ vā bhogaṃ phātiṃ kātuṃ."
msgstr ""
"A shopkeeper who has three factors is able to acquire more wealth or to "
"increase the wealth they’ve already acquired."

msgctxt "an3.19:3.2"
msgid "Katamehi tīhi?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.19:3.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, pāpaṇiko pubbaṇhasamayaṃ sakkaccaṃ kammantaṃ adhiṭṭhāti, "
"majjhanhikasamayaṃ … pe … sāyanhasamayaṃ sakkaccaṃ kammantaṃ adhiṭṭhāti."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a shopkeeper carefully applies themselves to their work in the "
"morning, at midday, and in the afternoon."

msgctxt "an3.19:3.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, tīhi aṅgehi samannāgato pāpaṇiko bhabbo anadhigataṃ vā "
"bhogaṃ adhigantuṃ, adhigataṃ vā bhogaṃ phātiṃ kātuṃ."
msgstr ""
"A shopkeeper who has these three factors is able to acquire more wealth or "
"to increase the wealth they’ve already acquired."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an3.19:4.1"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tīhi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu bhabbo "
"anadhigataṃ vā kusalaṃ dhammaṃ adhigantuṃ, adhigataṃ vā kusalaṃ dhammaṃ "
"phātiṃ kātuṃ."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, a mendicant who has three factors is able to acquire more "
"skillful qualities or to increase the skillful qualities they’ve already "
"acquired."

msgctxt "an3.19:4.2"
msgid "Katamehi tīhi?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.19:4.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu pubbaṇhasamayaṃ sakkaccaṃ samādhinimittaṃ "
"adhiṭṭhāti, majjhanhikasamayaṃ … pe … sāyanhasamayaṃ sakkaccaṃ "
"samādhinimittaṃ adhiṭṭhāti."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant carefully applies themselves to a meditation subject "
"as a basis of immersion in the morning, at midday, and in the afternoon."

msgctxt "an3.19:4.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, tīhi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu bhabbo anadhigataṃ "
"vā kusalaṃ dhammaṃ adhigantuṃ, adhigataṃ vā kusalaṃ dhammaṃ phātiṃ kātun”ti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant who has these three factors is able to acquire more skillful "
"qualities or to increase the skillful qualities they’ve already acquired.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.19:4.5"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
